description: Brand new Samsung memory card. Compliant with the SD Specification Version 2.00. Versatile - when combined with the adapter, can be used as a full-size SDHC card. 16GB storage for more music, videos, pictures, games, and applications. Compatible with microSDHC host devices; not compatible with standard microSD-enabled device/readers. SDHC Class10 compliant. Fully compatible with the SD 2.0 Standard. Supports Micro SDHC devices and cardreader. Supports Content Protection for Recordable Media (CPRM). Security level complies with Secure Digital Music Initiative (SDMI). Compliant with RoHS requirement. Lifetime Warranty.
title: Samsung 16GB Class 10 MicroSDHC High Speed Memory Card with Komputerbay SD adaptor and High Speed USB Reader
